thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by COLLEEN

author: COLLEEN
title: COLLEEN
text:
My car was pre booked but the process at the airport was somewhat marred due to computer malfunction - unfortunately, it seemed to be 'one of those days'!
However, from there on, there were no issues. The car drove like a dream and caused no issues. Returning the car at the airport, also went smoothly.
